00:41:52.920 --> 00:41:53.440
Jom pergi.

00:41:53.440 --> 00:41:54.770
Terima kasih, Kapten Qin!

00:41:54.880 --> 00:41:55.810
Cepatlah.

00:41:56.110 --> 00:41:56.640
Jom pergi.

00:41:57.280 --> 00:41:57.920
